extends base

block content
    section.hero(style='background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)), url(/img/bg-img/career.webp);')
        .sloggan
            h1 Careers
            p At OvichMedia, we combine the common and the exceptional minds <br> to think critically and share our stories.
        a(href="#" class="arrow-down" aria-label="Arrow down")
            i.fa-solid.fa-chevron-down
    section.container 
        section.career
            .career-img
                img(src="/img/mission3.webp", alt="OvichMeia Careers")
            .content 
                h1 Be part of a group that shares talent.
                p Join our community of exceptional minds that can help you make your career take you up to the next level. Find your creative side with us and start writing your next chapter while you stay informed about the latest career opportunities that may fit your skills. Start writing your story now with us. Subscribe to receive more news and updates.
        section.career
            .career-img
                img(src="/img/mission1.webp", alt="OvichMeia Careers")
            .content 
                h1 Begin your story with us
                p At OvichMedia, we bring together the ordinary and the extraordinary minds to challenge themselves and be part of the story we create. Join our team and be part of an organization that challenges the norm through innovation and creativity.